Movies about writers - 10 movies about writers we must absolutely watch 
17-3-2017 
There’s one thing to read about a writer and experience his dilemmas with expression, and then there’s watching him prancing about the screen in all his gloom and glory. But whichever may be the medium of exhibition, we as readers are always game to get a glimpse of the writer’s life. Cinemas have time and again tried to tell their stories and with much success. We have selected 10 of the best movies that depict the immortal spirit of authors and their lives. 
